attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Loft/one bedroom with high ceilings and open layout at the Bigelow School with PARKING! Large living/dining area with alcove for sitting area or work from home office option. Fully applianced kitchen with granite counters, stainless appliances and wood cabinets. Lofted bedroom has hardwood floors, walk-in closet and updated bathroom. Close to the West Broadway bus and Broadway Red Line T stop. Around the corner from West Broadway's numerous restaurants, shops, etc. Private storage closet, washer/dryer room, package area, bike storage and professional management round out this excellent sales offering. An excellent choice for a first-time buyer.
